Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:08.14,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}在謎團重重的此世之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.15,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}將橫行的棋子落下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.69,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}If I could burn it all down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:15.82,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}尋覓不見出口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.49,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HEFF1EA&\bord0}深切祈求的心願
